#

Peanut Butter Bacon Burger

25 min
$12.99
750 kcal
Difficulty: 15%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

PeanutsDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

Comfort FoodGrillingQuick Meal

Description

A mouthwatering combination of savory bacon, creamy peanut butter, and juicy beef that takes the classic burger to an exciting new level!

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • bacon: 4 slices
  • cheddar cheese: 4 slices
  • burger buns: 4
  • peanut butter: 1/4 cup
  • lettuce: 1 cup
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • pickles: 1/2 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
